<recipe>
<title>
Oatmeal Cookie Overnight Oats
</title>
<details>
PREP TIME: 5 minutes
TOTAL TIME: 5 minutes
SERVINGS: 2
</details>
<ingredients>
1 c . QuakerÂ® Old Fashioned Rolled Oats
1 c . 1% lowfat milk
1/4 banana mashed
1 tsp . brown sugar
1/2 tsp . ground cinnamon
1/4 tsp . ground nutmeg
Raisins
Nuts
</ingredients>
<instructions>
In a small bowl, stir together oat, milk, mashed banana, sugar, cinnamon, and nutmeg.
Cover, and refrigerate overnight.
In the morning, top with raisins and nuts.
Enjoy!
</instructions>
</recipe>
